#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Analyze return-addresses from dmalloc logfiles."
msgstr "dmaloc logfiles तः return-addresses विश्लेषयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extend_dmalloc</command> <group><option><replaceable>dmalloc-log</"
"replaceable> <command>binary</command></option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>विस्तार_dmalloc</command><group><option><replaceable> dmalloc-log "
"इति</replaceable><command> द्विचक्रीय</command></option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extend_dmalloc</command> will run <command>gdb</command>(1) to get "
"information on the return-addresses from a <command>dmalloc</command>(1) "
"logfile. Specifically it will examine any <literal>ra=</literal> lines and "
"try to get the corresponding line numbers"
msgstr ""
"<command>extend_dmalloc</command> <command>dmalloc</command>(1) logfile तः "
"return-addresses इत्यस्य सूचनां प्राप्तुं <command>gdb</command>(1) चालयिष्यति । "
"विशेषतः एतत् कस्यापि <literal>ra=</literal> रेखानां परीक्षणं करिष्यति तथा च "
"तत्सम्बद्धानि रेखासङ्ख्यानि प्राप्तुं प्रयतते"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The argument <option><command>binary</command></option> must be the binary "
"that generated the log <filename>dmalloc-log</filename>."
msgstr ""
"तर्कः<option><command> द्विचक्रीय</command></option> अवश्यं द्विचक्रिका भवितुमर्हति "
"यत् लॉग् जनयति स्म<filename> dmalloc-log इति</filename> ."

#. Tag: para
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "एषा उपयोगिता &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर विकास किट।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "टिप्पणियाँ"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may wish to direct the output from <command>extend_dmalloc</command> to "
"a file, since otherwise <command>gdb</command> seems to prompt for a return "
"as if you are at the end of a page."
msgstr ""
"भवान् <command>extend_dmalloc</command> इत्यस्मात् निर्गमं सञ्चिकां प्रति निर्देशयितुम् "
"इच्छति, यतः अन्यथा <command>gdb</command> इत्यनेन पृष्ठस्य अन्ते इव पुनरागमनं प्रार्थयति "
"इव"
